An interesting contrast:

@NicolaSturgeon is holding a press conference and taking questions from TV/radio broadcasters as well as (often hostile) newspapers like the Mail and Telegraph.

In contrast, @BorisJohnson is pre-recording a statement and not taking any questions.

It is now clearer than ever that the health of humanity is inextricably bound to the health of our planet .  
@BorisJohnson , we call on you to put a resilient economy , healthy communities and a thriving natural world at the heart of the #greenrecovery

https://t.co/eGQnnAJ6FF https://t.co/lWiEb9htoc

